

     *************   /usr/ipsc/examples/rmfort_vx/vx287node/README   ***********


   This directory contains example programs designed to allow you to run
   a typical VX application using a standard iPSC.  You can build two 
   programs in this directory:


	dlinpack.e - Double precision version of the standard linpack benchmark.

	slinpack.e - Single precision version of the standard linpack benchmark.


   All programs can be made using the makefile.  To execute, load the
   application onto the cube (e.g., type "load dlinpack.e").  For more
   information, see the iPSC USER'S GUIDE.
